01:24:45,353 --> 01:24:47,484
Kami sudah pikirkan semua
yang bisa dipikirkan.

1475
01:24:47,509 --> 01:24:49,253
Salib, bintang,
semanggi berdaun empat,

1476
01:24:49,278 --> 01:24:50,482
Huruf, angka, hieroglif.

1477
01:24:50,507 --> 01:24:52,638
Apa gunanya proyeksikan
bintang ke bulan?

1478
01:24:52,663 --> 01:24:54,082
