- Ya.

1566
01:29:31,866 --> 01:29:33,536
- Tanpa tahu apa-apa?
- Ya.

1567
01:29:33,560 --> 01:29:35,538
Bukankah harusnya ada
semacam jawaban...

1568
01:29:35,562 --> 01:29:36,974
