01:29:37,004 --> 01:29:38,407
Dialog Woodrow
tentang arti kehidupan.

1570
01:29:38,431 --> 01:29:41,100
- "Mungkin ada jawabannya."
- Benar. Itu pertanyaanku.

1571
01:29:42,525 --> 01:29:44,529
