berkembang."

1596
01:31:19,824 --> 01:31:22,871
"Maksudku, setidaknya itu
harapanku, tanpa seorang Ibu."

1597
01:31:24,219 --> 01:31:28,100
Aku bilang,
"Dia telat berkembang,"

1598
01:31:28,124 --> 01:31:33,157
"Tapi mungkin kurasa
kau harus gantikan aku."

1599
01:31:33,182 --> 01:31:35,238
Kau bilang, "Apa?"

1600
01:31:35,263 --> 01:31:37,782
