1610
01:32:25,337 --> 01:32:27,451
Sekarang aku First Lady-in-Waiting
untuk Queen Consort...

1611
01:32:27,475 --> 01:32:28,921
...dalam buah Withering Vine.

1612
01:32:28,946 --> 01:32:30,962
Kau melewatkan isyaratmu.
June dan si koboi...

1613
01:32:30,987 --> 01:32:32,669
...sudah bersiap di gerbong stasiun.

1614
01:32:32,694 --> 01:32:35,479
Mereka memasang perban
tangan pemain pengganti sekarang.

1615
01:32:36,665 --> 01:32:38,541
Itu kau.

1616
01:32:38,590 --> 01:32:40,507
Kita hampir memiliki
adegan bersama.

1617
01:32:40,532 --> 01:32:42,097
- Halo.
